<noinclude>
==Documentation==
Renders the game page sidebar with structured data pulled from Semantic MediaWiki properties.

This template is called automatically by <code><nowiki>{{GameEnd}}</nowiki></code>.

===Sections===
# '''Game details''' - Name, release date, platforms, developer, publisher, genre, theme, franchise, aliases
# '''Related content''' - Accordion sections for Characters, Locations, Concepts, Objects, People

===SMW Properties Used===
* <code>Has name</code> - Game title
* <code>Has release date</code> - Release date
* <code>Has release date type</code> - Release date type
* <code>Has platforms</code> - Platform links
* <code>Has developers</code> - Developer company links
* <code>Has publishers</code> - Publisher company links
* <code>Has genres</code> - Genre links
* <code>Has themes</code> - Theme links
* <code>Has franchises</code> - Franchise link
* <code>Has aliases</code> - Alternative names
* <code>Has characters</code> - Character links
* <code>Has locations</code> - Location links
* <code>Has concepts</code> - Concept links
* <code>Has objects</code> - Object links
</noinclude><includeonly>
<div class="gb-sidebar-section">
<div class="gb-sidebar-reviews">{{#invoke:ReviewQuery|renderSidebar}}</div>
<div class="gb-sidebar-section-header">Game details</div>
<div class="gb-sidebar-section-content">
<dl class="gb-game-details">

<dt>Name</dt>
<dd>{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|?Has name|default={{SUBPAGENAME}}}}</dd>

{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has release date#ISO
  |?Has release date type
  |format=list
  |template=DateDisplay
  |link=none
  |default=
  |intro=<dt>Release Date</dt><dd>
  |outro=</dd>
}}

<dt>Platform</dt>
<dd>{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|?Has platforms|format=list|link=all|sep=<br/>|limit=50}}</dd>

<dt>Developer</dt>
<dd>{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|?Has developers|format=list|link=all|sep=<br/>|limit=20}}</dd>

<dt>Publisher</dt>
<dd>{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|?Has publishers|format=list|link=all|sep=<br/>|limit=20}}</dd>

<dt>Genre</dt>
<dd>{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|?Has genres|format=list|link=all|sep=<br/>|limit=20}}</dd>

<dt>Theme</dt>
<dd>{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|?Has themes|format=list|link=all|sep=<br/>|limit=20}}</dd>

{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has franchises
  |format=list
  |link=all
  |default=
  |intro=<dt>Franchise</dt><dd>
  |outro=</dd>
}}

{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has aliases
  |format=list
  |link=none
  |default=
  |intro=<dt>Aliases</dt><dd>
  |outro=</dd>
}}
</dl>
</div>
</div>

<div class="gb-sidebar-accordions">

<div class="gb-accordion gb-accordion--open">
<div class="gb-accordion-header">Characters</div>
<ul class="gb-accordion-content">
{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has characters
  |format=list
  |link=all
  |limit=20
  |default=<li><em>None</em></li>
  |intro=<li>
  |outro=</li>
  |sep=</li><li>
}}
</ul>
</div>

<div class="gb-accordion">
<div class="gb-accordion-header">Locations</div>
<ul class="gb-accordion-content">
{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has locations
  |format=list
  |link=all
  |limit=20
  |default=<li><em>None</em></li>
  |intro=<li>
  |outro=</li>
  |sep=</li><li>
}}
</ul>
</div>

<div class="gb-accordion">
<div class="gb-accordion-header">Concepts</div>
<ul class="gb-accordion-content">
{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has concepts
  |format=list
  |link=all
  |limit=20
  |default=<li><em>None</em></li>
  |intro=<li>
  |outro=</li>
  |sep=</li><li>
}}
</ul>
</div>

<div class="gb-accordion">
<div class="gb-accordion-header">Objects</div>
<ul class="gb-accordion-content">
{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has objects
  |format=list
  |link=all
  |limit=20
  |default=<li><em>None</em></li>
  |intro=<li>
  |outro=</li>
  |sep=</li><li>
}}
</ul>
</div>

<div class="gb-accordion">
<div class="gb-accordion-header">People</div>
<ul class="gb-accordion-content">
{{#show:{{FULLPAGENAME}}
  |?Has people
  |format=list
  |link=all
  |limit=20
  |default=<li><em>None</em></li>
  |intro=<li>
  |outro=</li>
  |sep=</li><li>
}}
</ul>
</div>

</div>
</includeonly>
